snippet.title: Curious Expedition 2 - Steam Early Access Announcement | Thunderful Publishing
snippet.description:
Curious Expedition 2 is coming to Steam Early Access on June 17th, 2020!

Make sure to add the game to your wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1040230/Curious_Expedition_2/
